#3: The audience to speak the language to
is partners.

00:12:14.430 --> 00:12:16.230
Partners to me are very important.

00:12:16.230 --> 00:12:19.500
I as an insurance company have a lot of carriers.

00:12:19.500 --> 00:12:25.250
So some of them may be carriers that we have
that we can sell, whether it's Nation Wide,

00:12:25.250 --> 00:12:32.850
whether it's National Life or all these other
companies and then I have partners.

00:12:32.850 --> 00:12:40.250
I have partners that I deal with that, whether
